e-al-takabbur","tag-bad-deeds-al-sayyiat","tag-god-fearing-taqwa","tag-humility-al-tawadu","tag-manners-adab","tag-warning-al-nudhr"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-907","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":12923,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/17\/fear-allah-beginning-wisdom\/","url_meta":{"origin":34603,"position":0},"title":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud on Wisdom: Fear of Allah is beginning of wisdom","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 17, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu 'Iyas reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, would say in his sermons, \u201cThe best provision is mindfulness of Allah (al-taqwa), and the foundation of wisdom is the fear of Allah Almighty.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 712 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0625\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26911,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/12\/13\/ibn-masud-enjoining-gentle\/","url_meta":{"origin":34603,"position":1},"title":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud on Enjoining: He would not be mad at them, he was gentle","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 13, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ahmad ibn Hanbal reported: The companions of Ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, if they passed by people from whom they saw something they disapproved, they would say, \u201cTake it easy, may Allah have mercy on you.\u201d Source: al-Amr bil-Ma\u02bbru\u0304f lil-Khalla\u0304l 1\/25 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0645\u064e\u062f \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u062d\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0644\u064d \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0635\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0628\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17458,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/02\/ibn-masud-sins-mountain-fly\/","url_meta":{"origin":34603,"position":2},"title":"Ibn Mas&#8217;ud on Sins: Believers fears their sins, wicked do not","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 2, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Harith ibn Suwaid reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cVerily, the believer views his sins as if he were sitting under a mountain, fearing it will fall upon him. The wicked views his sins as if they were a fly passing over his nose.\" Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38216,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/09\/08\/umar-control-anger-whims\/","url_meta":{"origin":34603,"position":3},"title":"Umar on Taqwa: Fear Allah, control anger and desires","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 8, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Abdullah al-Khurasani reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cWhoever fears Allah does not vent his anger, and whoever is mindful of Allah does not do whatever he desires.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd li-Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 98 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064f\u0631\u0627\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064f \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064e\u0637\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0628\u0650 \u0631\u0636\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32729,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/11\/when-he-is-told-to-fear-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34603,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Taqwa: When he is told to fear Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the most beloved statement to Allah is for a servant to say, \u2018Glory be to You, O Allah, and Your praises. Blessed is Your name, exalted is Your majesty, and there is no God\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31840,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/08\/ibn-masud-friends-dhikr\/","url_meta":{"origin":34603,"position":5},"title":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud on Friends: Choose companions who remind you of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Ahwas reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cRemember Allah Almighty often. You must not accompany anyone unless they help you remember Allah Almighty.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 8998 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0623\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0635\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0646 \u0645\u0633\u0639\u0648\u062f \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647 \u0623\u064e\u0643\u0652\u062b\u0650\u0631\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0630\u0650\u0643\u0652\u0631\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0632\u0651\u064e \u0648\u064e\u062c\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e \u0648\u064e\u0644\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/34603","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=34603"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/34603\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href